    "body": "\n<div class=\"blog-post-body\">\n    <p>We are excited to announce that <a href=\"https://marketplace.microsoft.com/en-us/product/trenchdragonai.trenchonms?tab=Overview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0D41E1;\">Trench AI is now available on the Microsoft Marketplace</a>, bringing next-generation, AI-native SecOps directly into the Microsoft Azure ecosystem.</p>\n    <p>This means organizations can now deploy Trench AI seamlessly alongside Microsoft Sentinel or as a standalone AI SIEM accelerating threat detection, investigation, and response in minutes, not weeks.</p>\n\n    <h2 id=\"why-this-matters\">Why This Matters</h2>\n    <p>In the age of AI-driven attacks, <strong>velocity is everything</strong>.</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Attacks are deployed in <strong>minutes</strong></li>\n        <li>Detection still takes <strong>days or weeks</strong></li>\n        <li>Most breaches occur in this <strong>latency gap</strong></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Trench AI exists to close that gap.</p>\n    <p>Our mission is simple: Bring velocity to security teams to defend against AI-powered threats.</p>\n\n    <h3 id=\"for-teams-using-microsoft-sentinel\"><strong>For Teams Using Microsoft Sentinel</strong></h3>\n    <p>If you're already running Microsoft Sentinel, Trench AI acts as an intelligent automation layer on top:</p>\n    <h4><strong>What you get:</strong></h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li><strong>Real-time detections</strong> powered by AI agents (not static rules)</li>\n        <li><strong>Autonomous threat hunting</strong> across critical assets</li>\n        <li><strong>Enriched investigations</strong> with contextual intelligence</li>\n        <li><strong>Dynamic response workflows</strong> with automated playbooks</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Think of it as:</p>\n    <p>Turning Sentinel from a <strong>monitoring system → into an autonomous SecOps engine</strong> controlled by your lean security engineers or analysts.</p>\n\n    <h3 id=\"for-teams-without-sentinel\"><strong>For Teams Without Sentinel</strong></h3>\n    <h3 id=\"no-siem-no-problem\"><strong>No SIEM? No problem.</strong></h3>\n    <p>Trench AI offers a <strong>next-generation AI SIEM</strong> with built-in:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Threat Detection</li>\n        <li>Autonomous Hunting</li>\n        <li>Investigation Automation</li>\n        <li>Response Orchestration</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h4><strong>Native Integrations:</strong></h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Microsoft Azure services</li>\n        <li>Microsoft 365</li>\n        <li>Microsoft Entra</li>\n        <li>Log Analytics pipelines</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>All deployable <strong>in minutes from the Marketplace</strong>.</p>\n\n    <h2 id=\"what-makes-trench-ai-different\">What Makes Trench AI Different</h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"1-ai-native-threat-detection-mesh\">1. AI-Native Threat Detection Mesh</h3>\n    <p>Not rules. Not static correlation.</p>\n    <p>A <strong>dynamic detection layer</strong> powered by intelligent agents that:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Adapt in real-time</li>\n        <li>Learn from exposure and telemetry</li>\n        <li>Intent graph based detention system that continuously redefine anomalies from dynamic baselining</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3 id=\"2-80-secops-automation-out-of-the-box\">2. 80% SecOps Automation (Out of the Box)</h3>\n    <p>Trench AI is purpose-built for <strong>lean security teams</strong>:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Automates majority of Tier-1 / Tier-2 workflows</li>\n        <li>Eliminates alert fatigue</li>\n        <li>Lets teams focus on <strong>tuning intelligence,</strong> not on creating detection rules or chasing alerts</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3 id=\"3-built-for-velocity\">3. Built for Velocity</h3>\n    <p><strong>Velocity is the biggest risk to your data.</strong></p>\n    <p>Trench flips the equation:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>From <strong>weeks → minutes</strong> in detection</li>\n        <li>From <strong>manual → autonomous</strong> workflows</li>\n        <li>From <strong>reactive → real-time defense</strong></li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2 id=\"get-started-in-minutes\">Get Started in Minutes</h2>\n    <p>With Microsoft Marketplace integration, you can now:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Deploy Trench AI instantly</li>\n        <li>Integrate with existing Azure &amp; security stack</li>\n        <li>Start automating detections and response workflows immediately</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>AI has fundamentally changed the <strong>speed of attacks</strong>. Security teams can no longer rely on legacy SIEMs and manual workflows to keep up.</p>\n    <p>Trench AI delivers what’s missing: <strong><em>velocity with intelligence</em>.</strong></p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Autonomous agents</li>\n        <li>Real-time detections</li>\n        <li>Intent-graph driven intelligence</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n"
